---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Meridian" description="How Meridian Digital collects, uses, and protects your information.">

  <section class="bg-dark py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <p class="text-accent text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-semibold text-hero-text leading-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-muted text-lg">Last updated: March 1, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 prose prose-slate max-w-none">

      <div class="space-y-12 text-light-text leading-relaxed">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3">Who we are</h2>
          <p>Meridian Digital LLC operates bymeridian.com and the Meridian client platform. We provide AI-assisted SEO services to businesses. Questions about this policy can be sent to <a href="mailto:jeremy@bymeridian.com" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">jeremy@bymeridian.com</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3">What we collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We collect only what we need to run our service:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
            <li><strong class="text-dark">Contact form submissions</strong> — name, email, and message when you reach out through our site</li>
            <li><strong class="text-dark">Client account information</strong> — login credentials for the Meridian client platform (passwords are hashed and never stored in plain text)</li>
            <li><strong class="text-dark">Site analytics</strong> — we may use basic analytics to understand how the site is used (page views, referral sources). No personally identifiable information is attached to this data.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3">How we use it</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>To respond to your inquiry</li>
            <li>To provide you access to the client platform</li>
            <li>To send you reports and communications related to your engagement</li>
            <li>To improve the site and our services</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">We do not sell your data. We do not share it with third parties except where required to deliver the service (e.g., email delivery).</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3">Client site data</h2>
          <p>As part of delivering SEO services, we connect to your Google Search Console and Google Analytics 4 accounts. This data is used exclusively to produce reports and recommendations for your account. It is not shared, sold, or used for any other purpose.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3">Cookies</h2>
          <p>The public website does not use tracking cookies. The client platform uses a session cookie to keep you logged in. This cookie expires after 8 hours and contains no personally identifiable information beyond your client ID.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3">Data retention</h2>
          <p>We retain contact form submissions for up to 12 months. Client platform data is retained for the duration of your engagement plus 90 days. You can request deletion at any time.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3">Your rights</h2>
          <p>You can request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal data we hold about you. Email <a href="mailto:jeremy@bymeridian.com" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">jeremy@bymeridian.com</a> and we'll respond within 5 business days.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3">Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>If we make material changes, we'll update the date at the top of this page. We won't notify you by email for minor edits.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
